      "text": "Bet Gideans fazzija us teem : Es ne gribbu pahr jums waldiht / neds arri mans Dehls pahr jums waldihs/tas KUNgs pahr jums waldihs."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Gideans fazzija us teem: Es praffischu no jums kahdu Lee-ta / dohdeet man ikkatrs weenu Auschu-Sprahdst no juhsu Lau-pijuma/ jo teem bij selta Auschu-Sprahdses/ tapehz ka tee Isma-eliteri bija."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee fazzija: Mehs doh-fim / un tee isplattija kahdu Drehbi/ un mette us turren ik-kursch weenu Auschu-Sprahdsi no fawa Laupijuma."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to selta Auschu-Sprahdsu Swars / ko wiꞥsch bij praffijs bija tuhksfsocht un sep-tinfints Selta Sihketi / bes tahm Sprahdsehm un Schkeh-Dehm/ un Purpura Drehbheim / kas teem Midijaniteru Kehut-neenu bij Muggurâ bijuschas / un bes tahm Kallu-Gaitehm/ kas pee winno Raimeetu Kakleem bijuschas."
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Gideans darrija no ta weenu Eetodu / un eezeble to eekfs Owrn sawu Pilstahtu/un wiss Israëls maukoja tur tam pakkat/ un tas ktua Gideanam/ un winna Nammam par Slas-Walgu."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta tappe tee Midijanite ri pasemmoti preeksch Israëk Behrueem/ un ne pazehle wair sawu Galwu / un ta Semmi dusseja tschetrdefmits Gaddus kamehr Gideans dsihwoja."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jerub-Baäls/ Joaf Dehls / nogahje / un dsihwoj sawâ Ramunâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Gideanam bija sep-tindefmits Dehlu/ kas no winna Gurneem nahkutchi/ jo winnaan bij dauds Seewas."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna Sahnu-Seewa/ kas Sikeinâ bija/ dsemidej winnam arridsan weenu Dehlu un wiꞥsch nosauze winna Wahrdü Abimeleks."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Gideans/ Joafa Dehls nomitre labbâ Wezzumaâ/un tap-pe aprakts eeksch sawa Tehwa Joafa Kappa / eeksch Owras t Esriteru Tehwa."
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad Gideans bija ne mirris / tad atgreezahs Israëk Behrni/ un maukoja teem Baälim pakkat/ un eezeblahs to Baäl-Beritu jew par Deeivu."
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Israëka Behrni ne aminneja to KUNGU sawu Deewu/ kas tohs no wisfu Eenaids neeku Rohkas wifsapkahrt bisglahbis."
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee ne darrija ne kadu Schehlastibu pee Jerub-Baalâ/ tas irr Gideana Namimu pehz wisfu Labbumu/ ko winsc pee Israëta bij darrijs."
    }
  ],
